caption:
Not to be dramatic but this steak & eggs was one of the best breakfast dishes I’ve ever had. Was blown away by the breakfast at @forfive!! They offer so much more than just coffee, & it’s the perfect place to grab breakfast with a friend or even work remotely from! Absolutely delicious 🍳🥩🤤🤤

- Steak & eggs with hashbrowns: skirt steak, 2 eggs any style, chimichurri sauce, hashbrowns, toasted sourdough, romesco sauce 
- 24-hour Oatmeal: Overnight oats, strawberry jam, seasonal fruits, caramelized walnuts, pumpkin seeds, flax + hemp + chia seeds, honey, cashew butter
- Apple pie & oreo cookie (unreal)
- Vanilla oatmilk lattes
